{"id":124123,"type":6,"name":"小李飛刀 (1982)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/92/ec/124123_jzA27.jpg","summary":"中華電視台於1982年也將《多情劍客無情劍》改編成電視劇《小李飛刀》，共16集，韋辛製作，衞子雲扮演李尋歡，周雅芳扮演小神通，龍傳人扮演阿飛。\r\n\r\n1982年台湾华视版电视剧《小李飞刀》由卫子云、王美力主演。\r\n讲述了明朝中期成化年间，厌倦了官场世俗的文武全才李寻欢遇难之际被武林高手龙啸云相救，李寻欢和林诗音彼此相爱，但是龙啸云为了复仇对李寻欢横刀夺爱，迫使李寻欢远走他乡。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>小李飞刀</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16933\">衛子雲</a>、龍傳人、周雅芳、王美力、陳小慧</li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/16710\">張振寰</a>、<a href=\"/person/16660\">張復建</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>16</li><li><span>开始: </span>1982年</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>臺灣</li><li><span>电视台: </span>中華電視台</li><li><span>监制: </span>韋辛</li>","collection":{"dropped":1},"eps":[{"id":476395,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476395","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476396,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476396","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476397,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476397","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476398,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476398","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476399,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476399","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476400,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476400","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476401,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476401","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476402,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476402","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476403,"url":"http://bgm.